title: RSC Polymer Chemistry Series [Updated at 2016.02.28]
description:
ISSN: 2044-0790

Polymer chemistry is a vast research area and with so many papers published on the topic, it's hard to know where to start and what papers to read. With contributions from leading experts across the world, each book in the series covers key themes in polymer chemistry research for graduate level students and above. The perfect introduction to key topics giving the reader the knowledge to continue their work
